%% Order.status values — DB + buy_service.py comments
%% Transitions from buy.py, buy_service.py, socketio_gateway.py (_insert_machine_event), omise webhook

stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> pending_payment : create_pending_order\nor upgrade_draft

    pending_payment --> cancelled : POST /api/buy/cancel\n(success)
    pending_payment --> payment_failed : Omise fail / webhook fail\nbuy.py + webhook
    pending_payment --> paid : charge successful\n(webhook / checkout / mock-pay / status reconcile)

    paid --> dispensing : job.state DISPENSING\n(socketio_gateway)
    paid --> completed : job.state DONE\n(if no DISPENSING event)
    paid --> dispense_failed : deduct_stock / agent HTTP fail\n(buy.py) or job.state ERROR

    dispensing --> completed : job.state DONE
    dispensing --> dispense_failed : job.state ERROR

    dispense_failed --> refunded : _auto_refund success\n(socketio ERROR path)
    dispense_failed --> dispense_failed : refund fails\n(manual per logs)

    completed --> [*]
    cancelled --> [*]
    payment_failed --> [*]
    refunded --> [*]

    note right of pending_payment
        charge_id may be draft_* until
        upgrade to Omise charge id
    end note
